<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Ella Rises empowers young women to pursue higher education through
      multicultural programs rooted in mariachi, ballet folklorico and STEAM.
      Through hands on experiences and Latina mentors, girls build confidence,
      discover new pathways and learn to value their spiritual and cultural
      heritage.
    </p>
    <p>
      As girls move through the Ella Rises experience, they are encouraged to
      envision themselves in college, in meaningful careers and as leaders in
      their families and communities.
    </p>
